  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive (Home appliances)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a leading player in <strong>Kitchen Appliance Industry.</strong> They are looking for a Sales Executive to join their Sales Team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the <strong>East area</strong> – easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Drive growth and achieve monthly retail sales targets through effective management of the retail sales channel.</li><li>Develop and implement strategic sales plans to expand the company’s customer base and strengthen market presence.</li><li>Conduct sales training for dealers’ sales teams, covering retail business processes, daily sales operations, and customer management.</li><li>Analyze the strengths and gaps within the dealer network to effectively assign tasks to sales and marketing executives.</li><li>Oversee sales administration and monitor individual as well as team sales performance.</li></ul><p></p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Sales & Marketing/ Retail Management/ Business or a related field.</li><li>B2B sales experience strongly preferred</li><li>Must possess own vehicle (car) with a valid Class 3 Driving License</li></ul><p><strong>About The Role: </strong></p><ul><li>Basic + Commission Up to $4,000 + Car Allowance </li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R25157233</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Loh Pooi Keng</li></ul>",
